  "description": "<b>索尼周四在官方开发者网站上宣布，已启动“开放SmartWatch”项目(Open&#160;SmartWatch&#160;Project)，允许开发人员在索尼SmartWatch智能手表上开发和安装替代软件。</b>此前，开发人员可以通过索尼Add-on&#160;SDK为SmartWatch开发应用。但“开放SmartWatch”项目将索尼SmartWatch变成一款完全开放的设备，通过提供技术细节和说明，它允许高级开发人员开发替代性固件。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d3d341d/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240975.htm&amp;t=%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%A8%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%EF%BC%9A%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%96%B9%E5%9B%BA%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240975.htm&amp;t=%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%A8%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%EF%BC%9A%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%96%B9%E5%9B%BA%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240975.htm&amp;t=%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%A8%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%EF%BC%9A%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%96%B9%E5%9B%BA%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240975.htm&amp;t=%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E6%94%BE%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%A8%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%EF%BC%9A%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%96%B9%E5%9B%BA%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.co